The '''Austrian Cycling Federation''' or '''ORV''' (in [[German language|German]]: ''Österreichischer Radsport-Verband'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Austria]].

The ORV is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].

