{{Infobox country at games | NOC = JPN | NOCname = [[Japanese Olympic Committee]] | oldcode = | year = 1974 | date = | games = Asian Games | location = [[Tehran]] | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | officials = | gold = 72 | silver = 51 | bronze = 49 | rank = 1 | appearances = auto | seealso = | website = }}
'''[[Japan]]''' participated in the [[1974 Asian Games]] held in [[Tehran]], [[Iran]] from September 1, 1974 to September 16, 1974. This country was ranked 1st with 72 gold medals, 51 silver medals and 49 bronze medals with a total of 172 medals to secure its top spot in the medal tally.<ref>[http://www.ocasia.org/7AG.asp 1974 Asian Games medal tally] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060711210717/http://www.ocasia.org/7AG.asp |date=2006-07-11 }}</ref>
