'''Jossimar Orlando Calvo Moreno''' (born 22 July 1994) is a Colombian male [[artistic gymnast]] and part of the national team. He participated at the [[2014 World Artistic Gymnastics Championships]] in Nanning, China.<ref>{{cite web |title=2014 World Gymnastics Championships athletes – Jossimar Orlando CALVO MORENO |url=http://gym.longinestiming.com/File/00000D00020000FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF00 |work=longinestiming.com |date= |accessdate=27 January 2016}}</ref> At the [[2015 Pan American Games]] he won three individual gold medals.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.panamericanworld.com/en/athlete/jossimar-calvo|title=Jossimar Calvo|publisher=PanamericanWorld|accessdate=31 March 2017}}</ref>

